2003-11-11  Jody Goldberg <jody@gnome.org>

	* utils/go-pattern.c (go_pattern_selector) : add auto support.

	* utils/go-marker.c : move the default handling where it belongs.

	* utils/go-color.c (go_color_to_gdk) : new.

