2003-10-18  Jody Goldberg <jody@gnome.org>

	* graph/gog-chart-impl.h : Inherit from GogOutlinedObject and use the
	  padding there.
	* graph/gog-graph-impl.h : ditto.
	* graph/gog-label.c : ditto.
	* graph/gog-legend.c : ditto.

